ValueType Name: The name of the valuetype of a variable that you would like to include in your ontology schema.
Belongs to Ontology: If the valuetype already exists in an ontology below, select the ontology from the dropdown menu. Otherwise, please leave blank.
Domain: Please enter the term that the relationship starts from. (Example: If you would like to define the relationship that a tool term "outputs" an image term, select the tool term).
Range:
Please enter the value type you would like to attach to the term
*Only fill out for Data Property relationships*
Definition of Property: Please provide the definition the relationship. For reccomendation on a definition, search the term in https://schema.org. If the term is already in a selected ontology, please leave blank.
Logical Axioms:
Please provide any logic you would like to attach to your term. For information and examples on logical axioms, please visit https://www.w3.org/TR/daml+oil-axioms/ 
*Optional*
Alternative Name(s):
Please provide any alternative names for the relationship in the literature.
*Optional*
